<plot>"Bingo: Faith, Hope &amp; Charity." Actress Jackie Burroughs hosts this quirky look at the not-so-innocuous world of bingo. Canadians spend 10 times as much on bingo per capita as Americans. Meet bingo addicts, along with the promoters and charities that depend on bingo for cash. Bingo is the dark angel of charity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?071278</url></doc>
